column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra,p.dec,p.petror9#_r, p.dered_u, p.dered_g, p.dered_r, s.z as z_spec, s.zErr, zns.nvote, zns.p_el as elliptical, zns.p_cs as spiral   FROM Galaxy as p    JOIN ZooNoSpec AS zns ON p.objid = zns.objid    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE p.clean=# and zns.nvote >= #  AND zns.p_cs > # AND p.petror9#_r > #
